flowchart TD
    SPLASH["🌟 Splash Screen"] --> CHECK{First launch?}
    CHECK -->|Yes| ONBOARD["📖 Onboarding"]
    CHECK -->|No| AUTH{Logged in?}
    ONBOARD --> LOGIN
    AUTH -->|No| LOGIN["🔐 Login Screen"]
    AUTH -->|Yes| HOME

    LOGIN --> SIGNUP["📝 Sign Up"]
